

                                        CONTROL STATEMENTS
—-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Control  statements are used to control the execution flow of the programme
In java there are 3 types of control statements
			1.DECISION MAKING STATEMENTS
			2.LOOPING STATEMENTS
			3. SWITCH /JUMPING STATEMENTS









DECISION MAKING STATEMENTS ➖
—----------------------------------------------------------
 There are 4 types of decision making statements 
				1.IF 
				2.IF ELSE
				3. ELSE IF 
				4.NESTED IF
