				LOOPING STATEMENTS
—-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
If user or programmer wants to execute set of lines of code n number of times then we have to use looping statements

In java there are 3 types 
While
Do while
For 

While loop ➖
—----------------------------
When the number of iterations is not fixed then we have to use while loop.
While loop is also known as “ entry controlled loop “
Syntax ➖
—-----------
