Q. WHAT IS THE DIFF BETWEEN WHILE AND DO WHILE
?
ANS ➖
—----
			WHILE 					DO WHILE

First it will check the condition		* first it will print the statement once
Then it will execute				then it will check the condition

Minimum iteration for while loop 0.            * minimum iteration for do while loop is 1
Entry controlled loop				* exit controlled loop
We cant use semicolon end of the while      * we have to use semicolon end of the do while loop
